data.description: Welcome home to Adelaide Road in Oldefield! Sitting on a premium lot w/views of natures goodness right from your own backyard!You are greeted by a covered front porch & luscious curb  light cascades through the main entry way & fills the home with a warm & cozy dream home aesthetic. Private office space featuring french door  flooring flows through the main living areas including the open concept kitchen featuring granite countertops,recessed lighting,bright white cabinets w/ farmhouse inspired pulls, stainless steel appliances & tiled backsplash. This home was made with entertaining in mind,spacious eat in & a great room with high ceilings and gas  floor guest suite with walk in closet and private access to the downstairs guest  the stairs, a loft space with recessed lights & LVP flooring that flow into your Master Suite w/tray ceilings and double door entry into your spa inspired master bath w/ soaking tub,sep.shower,dual vanity & walk in closet with custom storage system!Also upstairs an upgraded laundry space w/ custom folding table & cabinetry,2 bedrooms featuring their own custom woodwork upgrades and a shared hall bath with matching granite. Fully fenced back yard with covered patio, storage shed, & wireless sprinkler system in the front, back and sides of the home! Basically like new construction!
